## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="494f9-102">Die Eigenschaften "<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>" und "<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>" bestimmen, wie Benutzer Elemente in einem <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>auswählen können.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="494f9-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties together determine how users can select items in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="494f9-103">Wenn die <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> z. b. <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionMode.Single?displayProperty=nameWithType> ist und die <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> `Cell`ist, kann der Benutzer im <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>jeweils nur eine Zelle auswählen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="494f9-103">For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> is <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionMode.Single?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> is `Cell`, the user can select only one cell at a time in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span></span>  
  
